;
; Project Meridian — DEV-ONLY chibi_pill_body preview scene (story #747, epic #722).
; The root Node3D's script (chibi_body_preview.gd) builds the whole preview
; (environment, light, camera, and the AssembledCharacter chibi body on a slow
; turntable) in _ready, so this scene file stays trivial. Launch:
;   scripts/dev/run-client.sh --scene=res://scenes/dev/chibi_body_preview.tscn
; See chibi_body_preview_verify.gd for the automatable, no-render counterpart.
; NOT wired into the shipped menu — a dev tool, launched explicitly.

[gd_scene load_steps=2 format=3 uid="uid://dchibi747preview"]

[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scenes/dev/chibi_body_preview.gd" id="1_chibi"]

[node name="ChibiBodyPreview" type="Node3D"]
script = ExtResource("1_chibi")
